race.comment: GREAT ASPIRATIONS (1) has been plying his trade in town and will find this assignment much more to his liking. Has two wins and a second from four spins around this circuit and should be right there when the whips are cracking. SWEET PROPOSAL (3) got a well-deserved victory last time out and winning rider Van Der Hoven sticks in the stirrups. Can go back-to-back without surprising. PRETTY RHO (4) is better than recent efforts suggest and is drawn to get a soft run in transit from the inside marble. One for the exotics players. LISSARO (5) strips fitter third-up from the break and makes some appeal.
